Class Racer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Wall
      • Racer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Updatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bot
    public class Racer
extends Wall
implements Updatable
    A moving wall controlled by players and bots. It leaves particle trails when it moves and particle bursts when it collides. It behaves according to statistics provided by its model.
